  "texts": [
    "Definition 2.2.",
    "A representation π: A → B(H) satisfies the superselection criterion w.r.t.",
    "the vacuum representation π 1 if for any cone Λ, there is a unitary equivalence π| Λ ≃ u.e.",
    "π 1 | Λ of representations of A Λ.",
    "We will call such a representation an anyon representation."
  ],
